  • HTTP Routing Table

HTTP Routing Table

/RetrieveFacsimile | /RetrieveFilersSinceDate | /RetrieveFilersSubmissionDateTime | /RetrievePanelOfReporters | /RetrieveReportingPeriods | /RetrieveUBPRReportingPeriods | /RetrieveUBPRXBRLFacsimile
 
/RetrieveFacsimile
GET /RetrieveFacsimile Retrieve individual bank facsimile data
 
/RetrieveFilersSinceDate
GET /RetrieveFilersSinceDate Retrieve filers since a specific date
 
/RetrieveFilersSubmissionDateTime
GET /RetrieveFilersSubmissionDateTime Retrieve filers with submission timestamps
 
/RetrievePanelOfReporters
GET /RetrievePanelOfReporters Retrieve Panel of Reporters for a reporting period
 
/RetrieveReportingPeriods
GET /RetrieveReportingPeriods Retrieve available reporting periods for Call data series
 
/RetrieveUBPRReportingPeriods
GET /RetrieveUBPRReportingPeriods Retrieve UBPR reporting periods
 
/RetrieveUBPRXBRLFacsimile
GET /RetrieveUBPRXBRLFacsimile Retrieve UBPR XBRL facsimile
